error: `seeds = [...]` is Anchor syntax and is not supported here. Declare the seed layout on the account type with `#[seeds(b"prefix", field: Type, ...)]`, then bind the PDA on this field with `#[account(address = MyAccount::seeds(<args>))]`. The bump is derived and stored automatically.
